			<h1 class="remove-margin">Patch Notes</h1>
			<h3>Version 2.0. Changes include: </h3>
			<ol>
				<li>HTML structure has been simplified and converted, where possible, to semantic HTML.</li>
				<li>Style guide created and CSS updated and simplified in line with the new style guide.</li>
				<li>Converted all non-manuscript images containing text to HTML so as to be compatible with screenreaders and copyable by users.</li>
				<li>Brand new homepage with major design changes, such as a smaller, responsive header, a logo, larger font size and line height.</li>
				<li>Expanded the Demonstratives section of <a href="cases4.html" target="_blank">Strong Masculine Nouns</a> and added a grammar test.</li>
				<li>Increased the number of questions in the grammar test of each Cases module.</li>
				<li>Added the ability to load different quizzes of varying complexity levels on the same page. See example <a href="naf7.html#basicbutton" target="_blank">here</a>.</li>
				<li>Updated grammar tables so they are properly responsive on mobile.</li>
				<li>Added togglable info-box component to allow the addition of information without increasing visual complexity. See example <a href="oestart.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</li>
				<li>Added abbreviation tags to complex words so they can be hovered for explanatory tooltips.</li>
				<li>Added audio to the <a href="oestart.html" target="_blank">phonetics table</a> to demonstrate correct pronunciation.</li>
				<li>Created the <a href="advpronuncationguide.html" target="_blank">Advanced Pronunciation guide</a> to explain more complex aspects of the phonology.</li>
				<li>Added the <a href="weakverbs.html" target="_blank">Weak Verbs</a>, <a href="nafnouns.html" target="_blank">Strong Neuter and Feminine Nouns</a>, <a href="pronouns.html">Pronouns</a>, and <a href="adjectives.html">Adjectives</a> modules.</li>
				<li>Updated <a href="about.html" target="_blank">About Page</a> to reflect completion of Masters and transition onto the development of the project as a stand-alone learning resource.</li>
				<li>Created the <a href="history.html">timeline</a> for a general overview of the development of Old English.</li>
				<li>Created this patch notes page to track changes.</li>
				<li>Created the <a href="license.html" target="_blank">license page</a> for licensing and copyright info.</li>
			</ol>
